        "end_card_button_label_mobile": "",
        "transcript": "Setting: A scenic outdoor terrace with white stone railings overlooking a lush, wooded landscape at dusk.\n\n[Visual Description]: The video opens with Anjelica Roselyn standing in a garden setting, holding the floral \"Artist Series\" tote bag and a smaller white handbag. Text overlays: \"The Invisible Thread with Anjelica Roselyn, Spring/Summer 26.\"\n\nAnjelica: I think all women have the ability to connect with one another, whether you live in America or you live in London. We meet up, and we have so much in common. I'm really lucky to have a lot of close personal female friendships myself. And I just think it’s where we connect with each other—with the way we laugh, the way we share stories, the way we shop together. There's so much that we have in common.\n\n[Visual Description]: Anjelica is wearing a white button-down shirt over a white tank top, styled with a colorful silk headscarf and a chunky butterfly-themed necklace. She gestures expressively as she speaks.\n\nAnjelica: I’m Anjelica Roselyn and thank you for watching my Anne Klein Invisible Thread interview.\n\n[Visual Description]: Anjelica smiles warmly at the camera, standing against the backdrop of trees and the evening sky. The video cuts to the Anne Klein logo centered over a shimmering blue water background."
